    <briefdescription>
<para>库仑力与常数定义。 </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>使用国际单位制：  <formula id="0">\[
   \mathbf{F}_{12} = k_e \frac{q_1 q_2}{\|\mathbf{r}\|^3}\,\mathbf{r},\quad
   \mathbf{r} = \mathbf{x}_2 - \mathbf{x}_1,\quad
   k_e = \frac{1}{4\pi\varepsilon_0}
 \]</formula></para>
<para>示例： <programlisting><codeline><highlight class="keywordtype">use<sp/></highlight><highlight class="normal">kinds,<sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keywordtype">only</highlight><highlight class="normal">:<sp/>dp</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="keywordtype">use<sp/></highlight><highlight class="normal">vector3,<sp/></highlight><highlight class="keywordtype">only</highlight><highlight class="normal">:<sp/>vec3</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="keywordtype">use<sp/></highlight><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="namespacephysics" kindref="compound">physics</ref>,<sp/></highlight><highlight class="keywordtype">only</highlight><highlight class="normal">:<sp/><ref refid="namespacephysics_1a8471f5aa31ae8dc7f1fe597ad23e9404" kindref="member">coulomb_force</ref></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="keywordtype">type</highlight><highlight class="normal">(vec3)<sp/>::<sp/>x1,<sp/>x2,<sp/>F</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="keywordtype">real</highlight><highlight class="normal">(dp)<sp/><sp/><sp/>::<sp/>q1,<sp/>q2</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">x1<sp/>=<sp/>vec3(0._dp,<sp/>0._dp,<sp/>0._dp)</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">x2<sp/>=<sp/>vec3(0._dp,<sp/>0._dp,<sp/>1._dp)</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">q1<sp/>=<sp/>1.0e-6_dp;<sp/>q2<sp/>=<sp/>2.0e-6_dp<sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">!<sp/>库仑</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">f<sp/>=<sp/><ref refid="namespacephysics_1a8471f5aa31ae8dc7f1fe597ad23e9404" kindref="member">coulomb_force</ref>(x1,<sp/>q1,<sp/>x2,<sp/>q2)</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para><simplesect kind="see"><para>vector3::vec3 </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
    <programlisting>
<codeline lineno="1"></codeline>
